name: AI Sandora
description: The AI Sandora Token (AIS) is a utility token designed to power the AI Sandora ecosystem. Unlike general-purpose crypto tokens, AIS is purpose-built for AI agency projects, ensuring that value, governance, and innovation remain tightly focused on AI solutions, automation platforms, and enterprise-grade tools.
